[SN]TITLE[SN]
Gareth Bale plays football on Penarth pier

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
While his Real Madrid teammates have been competing at Brazil's World Cup, Wales' Gareth Bale was spotted playing for the camera much nearer home.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Bale, who moved to Spain last summer, was on Penarth Pier near Cardiff - the city where he grew up.
He is understood to be filming an advert for a sports network.
As fans gathered to catch a glimpse on Monday - the 24-year-old showed off some of the skills that have made him the world's most expensive footballer.
